title.narrative: SEL-MHE model, based on national mental health education guidelines, finalized and piloted

target.value: 2020:Model, including teaching and training materials and strategies, finalized for replication, through piloting in 5 pilot counties

actual.value: 2019:SEL model and resource refined and implemented in pilot schools. Knowledge sharing activities organized to support SEL within and outside pilot schools. Collaboration with MOE established to integrate SEL into pre-service teacher training and junior secondary schools in coming years.
